Stadium Ticket RESTful API for Linux/Unix

0.  To install prerequisite packages:

    scripts/install-prerequisites.sh

1.  To initialize the database schema:

    scripts/mysql.sh <sql/schema.sql

2.  To reset the database to a known state:

    scripts/mysql.sh <sql/reset.sql

3.  To run the unit tests:

    ./test_tickets.py

4.  To start the app:

    ./app.py

5.  To test the app:

    scripts/app-test.sh

6.  To stress test the app:

    scripts/load-test.sh

7.  To build a Docker container:

    docker-compose up --build

